=== 更新 ===
《彩虹六号：围攻》在发售后，进行了多次更新，除了修复游戏内的程序错误、改进游戏机制，像是增加了可以把多次“队友击杀”的玩家自动剔除对战的系统，以及在2016年8月上线的“[https://www.battleye.com/ Battleye] {{Wayback|url=https://www.battleye.com/ |date=20210513142148 }}”<ref>{{Cite web|title=BattlEye 常見問題與解答|url=http://support.ubi.com/zh-TW/faqs/000025213/BattlEye-FAQ|accessdate=2019-07-06|work=support.ubi.com|language=zh|archive-date=2019-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191201144911/https://support.ubi.com/zh-TW/faqs/000025213/BattlEye-FAQ|dead-url=no}}</ref>反作弊系统。<ref>[http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/12/16/ubisoft-releases-an-auto-kicker-targeting-rainbow-six-siege-team-killers UBISOFT RELEASES AN AUTO-KICKER TARGETING RAINBOW SIX SIEGE TEAM KILLERS] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/12/16/ubisoft-releases-an-auto-kicker-targeting-rainbow-six-siege-team-killers |date=20170503091023 }}.IGN.2015-12-16.[2017-08-20].</ref><ref>[https://www.gamespot.com/articles/rainbow-six-sieges-new-anti-cheating-tech-already-/1100-6442744/ Rainbow Six Siege's New Anti-Cheating Tech Already Going Strong, Has Banned Thousands] {{Wayback|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/rainbow-six-sieges-new-anti-cheating-tech-already-/1100-6442744/ |date=20170807235424 }}.GameSpot.2016-08-17.[2017-08-20].</ref>此外游戏也增加了多个追加下载内容（DLC）。育碧方面确认游戏“会有很长的生命周期并会为其提供长期的内容更新”。<ref>[http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/05/12/ubisoft-updating-rainbow-six-siege-for-a-long-time? UBISOFT UPDATING RAINBOW SIX SIEGE 'FOR A LONG TIME'] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/05/12/ubisoft-updating-rainbow-six-siege-for-a-long-time |date=20150514235646 }}.IGN.2015-05-12.[2017-08-20].</ref>游戏的追加下载内容是对所有玩家免费提供，不过购买了[[季票|季票]]的玩家可以提前一周使用追加下载内容中的新特勤干员并无需声望解锁。<ref>[http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-09-17-all-rainbow-six-siege-dlc-maps-will-be-free-ubisoft-confirms All Rainbow Six Siege DLC maps will be free, Ubisoft confirms] {{Wayback|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-09-17-all-rainbow-six-siege-dlc-maps-will-be-free-ubisoft-confirms |date=20170807235306 }}.Eurogamer.2015-09-17.[2017-08-20].</ref><ref name="SPass">[https://www.gamespot.com/articles/heres-everything-the-rainbow-six-siege-dlc-season-/1100-6432231/ Here's Everything the Rainbow Six Siege DLC Season Pass Gets You] {{Wayback|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/heres-everything-the-rainbow-six-siege-dlc-season-/1100-6432231/ |date=20201108092512 }}.GameSpot.2015-11-12.[2017-08-20].</ref>游戏的更新由育碧蒙特利尔和育碧位于德国的子公司[[Ubisoft_Blue_Byte|Ubisoft Blue Byte]]负责。<ref>[http://www.pcgamer.com/for-honor-will-be-on-show-at-the-pc-gamer-weekender/ For Honor will be on show at the PC Gamer Weekender] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/for-honor-will-be-on-show-at-the-pc-gamer-weekender/ |date=20170807234854 }}.PC Gamer.2017-01-16.[2017-08-20].</ref>2019年9月20日，[[育碧|Ubisoft]]宣布將在近期升級伺服器，主要是為了解決存在已久的[[DDOS|DDoS]]問題。<ref>{{Cite web|title=官方公告|url=https://steamcommunity.com/gid/103582791437849933/announcements/detail/1591383308583356504|accessdate=2019-09-21|author=|date=|format=|work=store.steampowered.com|publisher=|language=zh-cn}}</ref>2020年1月15日，游戏更新了“2020邀请赛之路”活动，正式为游戏增加了[[战斗通行证|战斗通行证]]机制，玩家可以通过游戏战斗获得一些装备，也可以通过购买战斗通行证获得更多的装备和奖励。<ref>[https://www.ubisoft.com/zh-tw/game/rainbow-six/siege/game-info/battlepass ROAD TO S.I. 2020: BATTLE PASS] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ubisoft.com/zh-tw/game/rainbow-six/siege/game-info/battlepass |date=20210226014122 }}.Ubisoft.2020-01-15.[2020-01-16].</ref>从2020年第三赛季的“暗影传承行动”起，[[育碧巴塞罗那|育碧巴塞罗那]]工作室开始承担游戏更新的主要职责。从2021年第一赛季“-{zh-hant:腥紅劫案;zh-hans:绯红劫案}-”开始，育碧取消了本作的季票机制，改为通过战斗通行证获得新干员以及游戏中的奖励。但是在时隔一年后，育碧于2022年第一赛季“惡鬼面紗”开始重新提供季票给玩家购买。

